Book My Show Requirements:

Actors: Theatres, Event Organisers, Customers (Viewers of the show/event)

Theatres: 
a) Add/Remove Theatres, 
b) Add/Remove Movies, 
c) Edit/Update/Remove Movie Timings, 
d) Provide Snacks buying Option.

Customers: 
a) Display Movies, 
b) Display Shows per Movie, 
c) Book a Show, 
d) Search using a Filter (Location based, Movie Based, Timing Based or combinations)  

Note: For now, Event Organisers is considered out of Scope. It may be considered in scope for the Version 2 of this Application. 
